16
00:03:36,294 --> 00:03:37,670
Dingin sekali!

17
00:03:38,338 --> 00:03:40,048
-Ada yang datang?
-Tidak, kosong.

18
00:03:49,724 --> 00:03:52,393
Pagi, Tuan Newcombe.
