00:03:56,064 --> 00:03:57,524
Senang bertemu denganmu.

22
00:04:14,874 --> 00:04:16,042
-Pagi.
-Pagi.

23
00:04:19,796 --> 00:04:21,047
Nona Penrose?

24
00:04:28,847 --> 00:04:30,223
Mari kita bersihkan.

25
00:04:35,395 --> 00:04:36,938
Bukankah kau terlalu pagi?

26
00:04:38,314 --> 00:04:39,691
Ini sudah 13.30, Sayang.

27
00:04:40,525 --> 00:04:41,609
Tidak.

28
00:04:42,944 --> 00:04:44,529
Astaga! Audisiku!

29
00:04:53,163 --> 00:04:54,581
Bajuku tak cocok semua.

30
00:04:55,665 --> 00:04:57,375
Kau cantik mengenakan
apa pun, Sayang.

31
00:04:59,169 --> 00:05:00,336
Ini.

32
00:05:01,129 --> 00:05:02,630
Bagaimana kalau ini?

33
00:05:07,302 --> 00:05:09,679
Di mana kau
letakkan... naskahku?

34
00:05:09,762 --> 00:05:11,264
Tunggu sebentar...

35
00:05:11,347 --> 00:05:12,474
Demi Tuhan.

36
00:05:13,057 --> 00:05:15,101
Sudah. Semoga sukses, Manis.

37
00:05:15,185 --> 00:05:17,187
Terima kasih,
Sayang, kau baik sekali.

38
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:19,147
Bagaimana nasibku tanpa dirimu?

39
00:05:27,071 --> 00:05:29,115
Mari kita bersenang-senang.

40
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,658
KEDAI MINUMAN BAR

41
00:05:45,423 --> 00:05:49,093
Wah, ternyata Ny. H yang cantik
dan pendampingnya yang tepercaya.

42
00:05:49,177 --> 00:05:51,054
Mau pesan apa? Pekan ini sukses.

43
00:05:51,679 --> 00:05:53,097
Dua port dengan lemon.

44
00:05:53,181 --> 00:05:55,308
Setiap pekan bisa
sukses jika kau bandar judi.

45
00:05:55,391 --> 00:05:57,894
Kau tidak salah, Sayang.
Dua port dengan lemon, tolong.

46
00:05:57,977 --> 00:06:00,647
Tapi karena kini kalian
menemaniku, aku mujur.

47
00:06:00,730 --> 00:06:03,775
Kau kira kami mau menemanimu
demi segelas, Tuan Archie?

48
00:06:05,193 --> 00:06:07,445
Yang dua ini mahir
menilai watak.

49
00:06:08,196 --> 00:06:09,280
Mereka menyukaimu, Ada Harris.

50
00:06:09,864 --> 00:06:12,826
Kenapa mereka
menemanimu jika sepintar itu?

51
00:06:12,909 --> 00:06:15,119
Kenapa kau
menemaninya? Dia pemarah.

52
00:06:15,829 --> 00:06:18,248
Kami bertemu pada sif
pertamaku membangun pesawat.

53
00:06:18,373 --> 00:06:19,958
Teman terbaikku sejauh ini.

54
00:06:20,041 --> 00:06:22,877
Masalah wanita ini
adalah selalu berkata jujur.

55
00:06:22,961 --> 00:06:24,462
Tak bisa menahan dirinya.

56
00:06:24,546 --> 00:06:26,214
Itu sangat disayangkan.

57
00:06:30,051 --> 00:06:31,970
Baik, jaga sikap
kalian, Ibu-ibu.

58
00:06:33,805 --> 00:06:35,140
Aku akan mengawasimu.

59
00:06:46,151 --> 00:06:48,528
Perang sudah lama usai.

60
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:51,114
Eddie tak akan pulang.

61
00:06:54,701 --> 00:06:56,077
Bukalah.

62
00:06:59,622 --> 00:07:00,665
Ya.

63
00:07:20,477 --> 00:07:22,979
TELEGRAF KANTOR
POS NY. ADA HARRIS

64
00:07:41,372 --> 00:07:42,999
"Yang terhormat Ny. Harris,

65
00:07:43,082 --> 00:07:47,295
kami mengirimkan barang
pribadi milik Sersan Edward Harris,

66
00:07:47,378 --> 00:07:50,340
yang diambil dari lokasi kecelakaan
di dekat Warsawa, Polandia.

67
00:07:50,965 --> 00:07:54,969
Sebagai akibat penemuan ini,
Sersan Harris kini dinyatakan...

68
00:07:56,221 --> 00:07:58,014
gugur dalam tugas

69
00:07:59,140 --> 00:08:01,142
pada tanggal 2 Maret 1944.

70
00:08:02,101 --> 00:08:06,481
Mohon menunggu kabar selanjutnya
dari Pusat Administrasi RAF."

71
00:08:07,982 --> 00:08:09,275
Astaga, Ada.

72
00:08:12,153 --> 00:08:14,322
Aku turut berduka.

73
00:08:16,074 --> 00:08:17,826
Seharusnya sudah kuduga.

74
00:08:20,203 --> 00:08:22,497
Dia pasti sudah
kembali jika bisa,

75
00:08:23,498 --> 00:08:24,874
dengan suatu cara.

76
00:08:28,628 --> 00:08:30,338
Baik,

77
00:08:30,421 --> 00:08:31,756
berarti sudah selesai.

78
00:08:34,424 --> 00:08:36,385
Bebas dan tak terikat.

79
00:08:55,071 --> 00:08:56,322
Baik, Sayang.

80
00:09:00,285 --> 00:09:01,870
Kuharap kematianmu cepat.

81
00:09:07,542 --> 00:09:08,751
Aku merindukanmu.

82
00:09:17,635 --> 00:09:22,348
Tidak, acara sorenya boleh saja,
tapi tak perlu sarapan pernikahan.

83
00:09:24,100 --> 00:09:27,353
Nyonya Harris, bisa
tolong ambil itu? Ya.

84
00:09:27,437 --> 00:09:29,439
Tidak, itu pemerasan.

85
00:09:29,522 --> 00:09:33,651
Kau harus jelaskan kepada mereka
bahwa kami tak mampu membiayainya.

86
00:09:33,735 --> 00:09:35,487
Tidak, tentu harus sampanye.

87
00:09:36,237 --> 00:09:37,947
Tolong periksa robekan,
seprai bagian atas

88
00:09:38,031 --> 00:09:41,910
Ingatkan mereka, Charles anggota
parlemen. Itu pasti bermakna.

89
00:09:43,077 --> 00:09:45,371
Ya. Sampai jumpa.

90
00:09:49,375 --> 00:09:52,128
Pesta pernikahan ini
akan menyengsarakan aku.

91
00:09:52,212 --> 00:09:54,255
Kau punya anak, Ny. Harris?

92
00:09:54,339 --> 00:09:58,343
Benar-benar pengeluaran
besar dari awal hingga akhir.

93
00:10:00,220 --> 00:10:01,346
Ya.

94
00:10:02,764 --> 00:10:06,184
Laksamana Dant yang malang harus
memberikan pengorbanan terbesar,

95
00:10:06,893 --> 00:10:09,771
berlayar menuju Christie's
dan pantai yang lebih nyaman.

96
00:10:09,854 --> 00:10:11,481
Pria mengerikan, kata orang.

97
00:10:12,565 --> 00:10:16,194
Omong-omong, Lady Dant, aku
bertanya-tanya apa kau bisa...

98
00:10:16,277 --> 00:10:19,113
Kami sudah amat lama
mengencangkan ikat pinggang,

99
00:10:19,197 --> 00:10:21,616
sungguh ajaib kami
masih bisa bernapas.

100
00:11:33,688 --> 00:11:35,440
Bukankah itu bagus?

101
00:11:35,523 --> 00:11:38,651
Aku bersumpah tak mau
menginjak Avenue Montaigne,

102
00:11:38,735 --> 00:11:41,779
tapi gara-gara pesta
pernikahan ini dan adat di Paris,

103
00:11:41,863 --> 00:11:44,073
begitu mataku
melihat Ravissante...

104
00:11:44,657 --> 00:11:46,576
-Ravissante.
-...aku terpesona.

105
00:11:47,243 --> 00:11:49,162
Pada harga £500.

106
00:11:49,913 --> 00:11:51,664
Lima ratus paun?
Untuk satu gaun?

107
00:11:52,207 --> 00:11:53,416
Lord Dant...

108
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:57,378
Aku tak keberatan mengakui
keuangan kami ketat belakangan ini,

109
00:11:57,462 --> 00:11:59,339
tapi saat aku mengenakan ini...

110
00:12:01,883 --> 00:12:03,134
hal lain tak penting.

111
00:12:04,385 --> 00:12:05,428
Lotte?

112
00:12:05,512 --> 00:12:07,222
Sekarang, cepat sembunyikan.

113
00:12:07,305 --> 00:12:10,642
Jangan sampai Lord Dant melihatnya
sebelum aku sempat membujuknya.

114
00:13:12,579 --> 00:13:13,955
Ravissante.

115
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:17,750
Karya Christian Dior.

116
00:13:48,573 --> 00:13:49,657
Selamat malam, Sayang.

