Aku menang!

135
00:15:09,445 --> 00:15:10,446
Tutup mulut!

136
00:15:10,530 --> 00:15:13,783
Kau harus ramah kepadanya.
Dia hanya menang taruhan.

137
00:15:17,912 --> 00:15:20,290
Ada, apa yang akan kau lakukan?

138
00:15:21,666 --> 00:15:22,917
Aku akan beli gaun.

139
00:15:23,585 --> 00:15:26,129
Gaun indah untuk
Pesta Dansa Legion.

140
00:15:26,212 --> 00:15:27,213
Ya.

141
00:15:27,922 --> 00:15:31,426
Sebuah gaun
Christian Dior dari Paris.

142
00:15:33,261 --> 00:15:34,512
Lima ratus paun.

143
00:15:39,350 --> 00:15:40,977
Berapa uang kemenanganmu?

144
00:15:41,060 --> 00:15:43,354
Gaun Dior Target £500,
Kemenangan Taruhan -£150

145
00:15:46,566 --> 00:15:48,151
Donasi -3 Shilling/6 Sen

146
00:15:49,611 --> 00:15:51,654
Masih ada tiket?

147
00:15:51,738 --> 00:15:52,864
Ke mana, Bu?

148
00:15:56,326 --> 00:15:57,827
Melajang, Nona Violet?

149
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:01,122
Aku tak mau membereskan
kekacauan pria.

150
00:16:04,918 --> 00:16:06,127
Pagi, Tuan Newcombe.

151
00:16:06,211 --> 00:16:07,253
Nyonya Harris.

152
00:16:07,337 --> 00:16:10,006
Kurasa kau belum bertemu
dengan Samantha, keponakanku.

153
00:16:10,089 --> 00:16:12,175
Belum. Belum sempat.

154
00:16:12,258 --> 00:16:13,510
Tuan Newcombe,

155
00:16:14,427 --> 00:16:16,638
jika kau kenal orang
yang butuh jasaku...

156
00:16:17,889 --> 00:16:19,682
Mungkin salah satu keponakanmu?

157
00:16:21,142 --> 00:16:23,853
Samantha, Ny. H ini
perwujudan kehati-hatian.

158
00:16:23,937 --> 00:16:26,815
Tak ada yang tahu dia pernah datang
tanpa melihat kilau kenop pintuku.

159
00:16:26,898 --> 00:16:28,274
Astaga, Giles!

160
00:17:22,996 --> 00:17:24,080
Terima kasih.

161
00:17:30,837 --> 00:17:32,380
JASA MENISIK TAK
TERLIHAT Ny. Ada Harris

